ComicInfo.Summary: TWISTORY STUDIOS presents PAOLO PARENTE'S pin-up girl & war machine universe like you have never seen. Issue #3 is the thrilling conclusion to the covert Allied mission to loot a castle deep behind enemy lines, and they inadvertently save the world from destruction. Meanwhile Soviet Commander Koshka Rudinova and her well-armored KV-47 robot team is on the run after discovery an Axis air patrol. Be sure not to miss the final of latest three-issue series from PAOLO PARENTE's ever-growing DUST universe. This time, it's DUST WARS!
ComicInfo.Title: Gunter Valley: Part Three
